This paper deals with a machine learning problem of multitask learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes an efficient algorithm to optimize the problem, which involves optimization and graph theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
